data.description: Whey rent? While you can own this house. Great for first time home buyer or investment property. Hard to find 1 level home under $374k located in a central area. 3 bedrooms, 1 bath. Quite neighborhood and convenience location. Minutes to bus line, freeway, shopping malls, groceries, schools and restaurants. Easy to commute to anywhere. Big backyard with large deck. Possibility of adding ADU at the back. Buyer to do due diligence. Open floor plan. Kitchen with eating bar. New exterior paint in 2021. New Water heater 2018. New concrete driveway. New Electrical panel. Double pane vinyl windows. Refrigerator, washer & dryer are included. Seller to provide 1-year Fidelity National Home Warranty at no cost to the buyer. [Home Energy Score = 2. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10194104]
